1
00:01:27,060 --> 00:01:35,980
[Zhan Zhao Adventures]

2
00:01:35,980 --> 00:01:37,980
[Episode 4]

3
00:01:56,260 --> 00:01:59,060
[West Bridge Dock]

4
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:25,690
Chief Zhong,

5
00:02:26,510 --> 00:02:27,700
are you here to watch the show today?

6
00:02:28,250 --> 00:02:30,260
I'm under the control of Zhan Zhao's Soaring Crane Skill.

7
00:02:30,940 --> 00:02:32,010
I can't move.

8
00:02:32,350 --> 00:02:33,170
What about the Iron Blood Guards?

9
00:02:33,440 --> 00:02:34,420
They've always followed the rule

10
00:02:34,420 --> 00:02:35,770
of not harming innocents.

11
00:02:36,350 --> 00:02:36,940
Today,

12
00:02:37,070 --> 00:02:38,940
they won't break that rule for Xiuluo Cult.

13
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:40,450
This isn't for me.

14
00:02:40,630 --> 00:02:42,050
It's for Master's great cause.

15
00:02:42,350 --> 00:02:44,900
If so, bring Master's command token.

16
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:45,660
You!

17
00:02:49,160 --> 00:02:50,010
Well, well.

18
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:52,050
Now I see.

19
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:54,730
You just want to play both sides and come out on top.

20
00:02:55,070 --> 00:02:56,140
I'm staying out of it

21
00:02:56,310 --> 00:02:57,860
because I don't want to fight you for the credit.

22
00:02:58,470 --> 00:02:59,380
Now

23
00:02:59,750 --> 00:03:00,540
all the credit

24
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:01,770
is yours.

25
00:05:22,180 --> 00:05:24,020
You won't even spare your own men?

26
00:05:24,350 --> 00:05:25,180
Yunying Sect

27
00:05:25,270 --> 00:05:27,220
only knows some qinggong tricks.
[*Light body technique]

28
00:05:27,350 --> 00:05:28,370
They'll never amount to much anyway.

29
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:29,810
Dying for me

30
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:32,330
would make his death worthwhile.

31
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:35,180
Don't move.

32
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:36,900
- Mother! - Sir!

33
00:05:37,410 --> 00:05:39,200
Please save my son.

34
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:40,150
One more step,

35
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:41,690
and I'll snap his neck.

36
00:05:42,550 --> 00:05:43,290
Sir.

37
00:05:45,500 --> 00:05:46,300
I'm begging you.

38
00:05:48,290 --> 00:05:51,210
Please save my son, sir!

39
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:54,180
Don't worry.

40
00:05:55,250 --> 00:05:56,510
I'll save him.

41
00:06:05,820 --> 00:06:07,540
[Yanling]

42
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:11,290
Zhan Zhao,

43
00:06:11,910 --> 00:06:13,540
you might run away with Soaring Crane Skill.

44
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:15,330
But if you use it to save that child,

45
00:06:15,790 --> 00:06:16,980
you may never leave this dock

46
00:06:16,980 --> 00:06:18,100
alive.

47
00:06:18,350 --> 00:06:19,330
By noon,

48
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:20,940
the poison in your body will flare up.

49
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:24,180
Without the protection of the Soaring Crane Skill,

50
00:06:24,830 --> 00:06:25,450
you'll

51
00:06:26,030 --> 00:06:27,130
die.

52
00:06:48,200 --> 00:06:49,130
I knew it.

53
00:06:49,520 --> 00:06:51,060
You wouldn't dare kill me.

54
00:06:51,880 --> 00:06:54,660
The great Southern Hero joined the imperial court

55
00:06:54,760 --> 00:06:56,010
and gained fame and status,

56
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:58,250
only to end up shackled by laws and rules.

57
00:06:58,880 --> 00:07:00,540
Isn't that laughable?

58
00:07:02,320 --> 00:07:04,690
You claim to uphold justice,

59
00:07:04,960 --> 00:07:06,980
yet you don't even have the courage to kill someone like me

60
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:09,210
and rid the world of evil.

61
00:07:12,220 --> 00:07:13,250
If Liu Hongyi

62
00:07:13,250 --> 00:07:14,810
sees you like this today,

63
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:15,980
he'll call you

64
00:07:16,080 --> 00:07:17,420
a coward.

65
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:19,350
I've planted over ten kinds of Xiuluo Cult poison

66
00:07:19,350 --> 00:07:21,200
in his body.

67
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:22,250
None of them

68
00:07:22,350 --> 00:07:23,620
will kill him right away.

69
00:07:24,440 --> 00:07:25,970
But they'll slowly melt away

70
00:07:25,970 --> 00:07:27,890
his organs.

71
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,770
He'll rot from the inside out

72
00:07:29,880 --> 00:07:32,250
until he turns into a puddle of blood.

73
00:07:59,640 --> 00:08:01,030
Serving evil

74
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:04,600
was never the Yunying Sect's way.

75
00:08:05,730 --> 00:08:07,190
Now that Mo Dao is dead,

76
00:08:08,030 --> 00:08:09,180
my master

77
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:11,270
can finally

78
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:12,770
rest

79
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:14,970
in peace.

80
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,570
Once you pass the farm up ahead,

81
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:30,450
you'll reach West Bridge Dock.

82
00:09:31,350 --> 00:09:32,610
After crossing that river,

83
00:09:32,710 --> 00:09:33,330
it'll be outside

84
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,690
Xiangzhou Prefecture's jurisdiction.

85
00:09:35,230 --> 00:09:36,540
[West Bridge Dock]
Yincheng Town

86
00:09:36,750 --> 00:09:37,810
is twenty li ahead.

87
00:09:38,280 --> 00:09:39,610
The Guanghua Army is stationed there.

88
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:41,940
Commandant Meng Kui is a friend of mine.

89
00:09:42,470 --> 00:09:43,380
He'll send men

90
00:09:43,630 --> 00:09:44,730
to escort me north.

91
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:46,450
If we can get a fast horse,

92
00:09:47,040 --> 00:09:47,940
we can reach the capital

93
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:49,780
in less than two days.

94
00:10:00,590 --> 00:10:01,300
Was he captured?

95
00:10:01,710 --> 00:10:02,210
Yes. We caught him.

96
00:10:38,710 --> 00:10:40,140
Have you searched him thoroughly?

97
00:10:40,830 --> 00:10:42,380
It wasn't on Zhan Zhao.

98
00:10:43,350 --> 00:10:44,010
I've sent men

99
00:10:44,010 --> 00:10:45,180
to track down the person traveling with him.

100
00:10:45,870 --> 00:10:46,810
Once he wakes up,

101
00:10:47,230 --> 00:10:47,970
we'll find a way

102
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:49,210
to make him reveal that person's whereabouts.

103
00:10:49,750 --> 00:10:51,020
You expect Zhan Zhao to talk?

104
00:10:52,110 --> 00:10:54,210
That's wishful thinking.

105
00:10:55,230 --> 00:10:56,260
Chief Zhong,

106
00:10:56,470 --> 00:10:57,780
rather than sitting here

107
00:10:57,870 --> 00:10:58,900
waiting for him to wake up,

108
00:10:59,470 --> 00:11:00,780
why not use your head

109
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:02,660
and look for clues instead?

110
00:11:03,680 --> 00:11:04,820
After Zhan Zhao was captured,

111
00:11:04,820 --> 00:11:05,510
I tightened inspections

112
00:11:05,510 --> 00:11:07,020
at every checkpoint.

113
00:11:07,350 --> 00:11:08,780
But we found no trace of his accomplice.

114
00:11:09,350 --> 00:11:10,970
At this point, other than waiting for him to confess,

115
00:11:11,230 --> 00:11:11,940
how else are we supposed to investigate?

116
00:11:12,830 --> 00:11:13,570
Commander Shao,

117
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:15,540
please enlighten me.

118
00:11:23,230 --> 00:11:25,610
Where did you find Zhan Zhao?

119
00:11:25,710 --> 00:11:26,160
My men ran into

120
00:11:26,160 --> 00:11:28,140
Zhan Zhao and his accomplice

121
00:11:28,230 --> 00:11:29,380
on the mountain road leading to West Bridge Dock.

122
00:11:29,860 --> 00:11:31,690
Afterward, I discovered

123
00:11:31,690 --> 00:11:32,970
that his hiding place

124
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,610
was in an abandoned granary near the dock.

125
00:11:35,870 --> 00:11:37,660
What did the person traveling with him

126
00:11:37,990 --> 00:11:38,810
look like?

127
00:11:39,350 --> 00:11:40,020
Wei Feng.

128
00:11:40,280 --> 00:11:40,570
Yes, sir.

129
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:46,780
Report to Commander Shao

130
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:48,900
what the person traveling with Zhan Zhao

131
00:11:48,990 --> 00:11:49,900
looked like.

132
00:11:49,990 --> 00:11:50,260
Yes, sir.

133
00:11:51,160 --> 00:11:52,140
Commander Shao,

134
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:54,450
that person appeared to be a young man around eighteen or nineteen.

135
00:11:54,990 --> 00:11:55,940
He was fine-featured

136
00:11:56,230 --> 00:11:57,090
and highly skilled in martial arts.

137
00:11:57,630 --> 00:11:58,660
The moment he attacked,

138
00:11:58,920 --> 00:12:00,660
we couldn't fight back at all.

139
00:12:01,280 --> 00:12:02,940
The weapon he used was very strange.

140
00:12:03,280 --> 00:12:04,210
It was all black

141
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:05,090
and looked like a swordbreaker.

142
00:12:14,350 --> 00:12:14,900
Commander Shao,

143
00:12:15,920 --> 00:12:16,900
Master specifically ordered

144
00:12:16,920 --> 00:12:17,610
that Zhan Zhao be taken alive.

145
00:12:18,280 --> 00:12:19,690
If you intend to kill him,

146
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:21,940
you'd best report it to Master yourself.

147
00:12:33,750 --> 00:12:34,450
It took great effort

148
00:12:34,560 --> 00:12:35,730
to capture Zhan Zhao at the dock.

149
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:37,660
Zhong Xiong stood by and did nothing,

150
00:12:37,750 --> 00:12:38,900
so we suffered many casualties.

151
00:12:39,110 --> 00:12:40,020
Even Mo Dao lost his life.

152
00:12:40,630 --> 00:12:41,300
I suspect

153
00:12:41,590 --> 00:12:42,420
Zhong Xiong may have tried

154
00:12:42,510 --> 00:12:43,540
to avoid pursuing the accomplice

155
00:12:43,630 --> 00:12:44,490
and stalled for time.

156
00:12:46,750 --> 00:12:48,020
Zhong Xiong

157
00:12:48,110 --> 00:12:49,020
thinks very highly of himself.

158
00:12:49,230 --> 00:12:50,300
Other than Master,

159
00:12:50,400 --> 00:12:52,060
he rarely respects anyone.

160
00:12:52,630 --> 00:12:53,380
This time,

161
00:12:53,630 --> 00:12:55,300
he was dragged to the dock

162
00:12:55,830 --> 00:12:56,940
under Zhan Zhao's control

163
00:12:57,400 --> 00:12:58,260
in full view of everyone,

164
00:12:58,830 --> 00:13:00,540
he had already lost all face.

165
00:13:00,830 --> 00:13:03,090
If he loses Zhan Zhao's accomplice too,

166
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:04,780
he'll have no way to answer for it.

167
00:13:05,280 --> 00:13:06,380
You're suggesting that...

168
00:13:12,400 --> 00:13:14,090
It's not that he refused to search.

169
00:13:14,560 --> 00:13:16,210
He's simply as foolish as you

170
00:13:16,400 --> 00:13:17,610
and doesn't know where to start.

171
00:13:21,470 --> 00:13:21,860
Hyah!

172
00:13:25,400 --> 00:13:25,780
Hyah!

173
00:13:29,280 --> 00:13:30,970
Zhong Xiong is a moron.

174
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:33,400
Zhan Zhao's accomplice

175
00:13:33,400 --> 00:13:34,810
was hiding in the granary,

176
00:13:34,990 --> 00:13:35,700
yet he still let him escape

177
00:13:35,700 --> 00:13:37,090
right under his nose.

178
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:41,660
Zhan Zhao's accomplice does possess impressive qinggong.

179
00:13:41,990 --> 00:13:43,450
Otherwise, these footprints wouldn't be so shallow.

180
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:45,380
But looking at them,

181
00:13:45,800 --> 00:13:47,450
one print is deep while the other is shallow.

182
00:13:48,510 --> 00:13:49,610
Could he have injured his leg?

183
00:13:57,510 --> 00:13:59,780
I believe this person may have left Xiangzhou.

184
00:14:00,400 --> 00:14:01,020
It can't be.

185
00:14:01,470 --> 00:14:02,380
Every road leading in and out of Xiangzhou

186
00:14:02,470 --> 00:14:03,490
has been sealed off.

187
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:04,730
Even with wings,

188
00:14:04,920 --> 00:14:05,540
he couldn't have escaped.

189
00:14:06,680 --> 00:14:07,420
Before the battle,

190
00:14:07,430 --> 00:14:08,540
we did seal off

191
00:14:08,550 --> 00:14:09,430
every checkpoint.

192
00:14:09,920 --> 00:14:11,380
But after capturing Zhan Zhao,

193
00:14:11,630 --> 00:14:12,850
there was one place we overlooked.

194
00:14:13,920 --> 00:14:14,540
West Bridge Dock?

195
00:14:15,040 --> 00:14:16,780
Zhan Zhao outfoxed Zhong Xiong.

196
00:14:17,630 --> 00:14:18,970
He predicted

197
00:14:19,400 --> 00:14:20,940
that once Zhong Xiong discovered

198
00:14:21,040 --> 00:14:22,730
the letter wasn't on him,

199
00:14:22,960 --> 00:14:24,860
he would assume Zhan Zhao fought desperately

200
00:14:24,950 --> 00:14:25,730
at West Bridge Dock

201
00:14:25,730 --> 00:14:27,000
to buy time

202
00:14:27,400 --> 00:14:28,730
for his accomplice

203
00:14:28,830 --> 00:14:29,450
to take the letter

204
00:14:29,560 --> 00:14:30,780
elsewhere.

205
00:14:31,590 --> 00:14:32,940
Zhan Zhao

206
00:14:33,280 --> 00:14:34,690
is truly

207
00:14:34,800 --> 00:14:35,540
smart.

208
00:14:36,280 --> 00:14:37,760
Even though he's gravely wounded

209
00:14:37,760 --> 00:14:38,850
and left alone,

210
00:14:39,920 --> 00:14:41,540
he still managed

211
00:14:41,540 --> 00:14:42,570
to toy with Zhong Xiong and his men.

212
00:14:43,280 --> 00:14:45,210
No wonder Liu Hongyi came to him.

213
00:14:46,160 --> 00:14:47,380
It's a pity.

214
00:14:48,040 --> 00:14:49,380
I'll never have the chance

215
00:14:49,920 --> 00:14:51,690
to spar with such a man.

216
00:14:58,110 --> 00:14:59,020
Even if we know

217
00:14:59,110 --> 00:15:00,420
his accomplice has a leg injury,

218
00:15:00,830 --> 00:15:02,380
finding a young man around eighteen or nineteen

219
00:15:03,040 --> 00:15:04,780
in the crowd

220
00:15:05,160 --> 00:15:06,210
is like searching for a needle in a haystack.

221
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:07,900
Not necessarily.

222
00:15:08,830 --> 00:15:09,610
Have you forgotten?

223
00:15:10,280 --> 00:15:11,250
That person carries

224
00:15:11,250 --> 00:15:13,380
a rare weapon.

225
00:15:13,990 --> 00:15:15,610
Do you already know who he is?

226
00:15:18,280 --> 00:15:19,060
Do you really think

227
00:15:20,040 --> 00:15:22,270
Zhan Zhao could've survived this long

228
00:15:22,270 --> 00:15:23,060
without Linglong Honey

229
00:15:23,440 --> 00:15:24,300
from Linglong Manor?

230
00:15:25,750 --> 00:15:26,330
Then that means...

231
00:15:28,400 --> 00:15:29,380
Head to West Bridge Dock.

232
00:15:29,800 --> 00:15:30,610
Cross the river and hunt them down.

233
00:15:33,710 --> 00:15:34,200
Move.

234
00:15:35,160 --> 00:15:35,540
Hyah!

235
00:15:38,560 --> 00:15:38,950
Hyah!

236
00:15:51,510 --> 00:15:52,540
She's gone?

237
00:15:52,750 --> 00:15:54,400
We had an argument yesterday,

238
00:15:55,040 --> 00:15:56,420
and she disappeared that evening.

239
00:15:56,510 --> 00:15:57,120
She knew

240
00:15:57,120 --> 00:15:58,390
I was coming today with the betrothal gifts.

241
00:15:58,830 --> 00:16:00,060
Did she run away to avoid the marriage?

242
00:16:00,800 --> 00:16:01,330
Uh...

243
00:16:01,330 --> 00:16:02,620
[Huo Tianxing, Master of Linglong Manor]

244
00:16:05,870 --> 00:16:07,260
I always believed

245
00:16:07,560 --> 00:16:08,610
no one meant more to us

246
00:16:08,710 --> 00:16:09,380
after all those years growing up together.

247
00:16:10,920 --> 00:16:12,380
Could it be she never felt the same way?

248
00:16:14,200 --> 00:16:14,730
Jizu,

249
00:16:15,280 --> 00:16:15,850
don't overthink it.

250
00:16:16,080 --> 00:16:16,730
Linglong

251
00:16:16,830 --> 00:16:17,380
probably ran off

252
00:16:17,390 --> 00:16:19,090
to stay with relatives for a while

253
00:16:19,200 --> 00:16:20,420
after I gave her an earful.

254
00:16:21,470 --> 00:16:22,490
The wedding won't be delayed.

255
00:16:46,990 --> 00:16:47,610
Have a nice day.

256
00:16:57,400 --> 00:16:58,140
Mister,

257
00:16:58,230 --> 00:16:59,020
your tea has gone cold.

258
00:16:59,110 --> 00:17:00,260
Let me get you a bowl of hot tea.

259
00:17:00,350 --> 00:17:00,900
No thanks.

260
00:17:01,280 --> 00:17:02,030
May I ask

261
00:17:02,080 --> 00:17:03,040
how to get to Yincheng Town?

262
00:17:03,280 --> 00:17:03,970
Yincheng Town?

263
00:17:04,790 --> 00:17:06,140
Head west

264
00:17:06,440 --> 00:17:07,290
for about twenty li, and you'll arrive.

265
00:17:07,600 --> 00:17:08,320
Look,

266
00:17:08,320 --> 00:17:09,380
it's getting dark.

267
00:17:09,600 --> 00:17:10,660
If you leave now,

268
00:17:10,960 --> 00:17:12,340
you won't find an inn for the night.

269
00:17:14,510 --> 00:17:15,140
Alright.

270
00:17:15,550 --> 00:17:15,900
Thank you.

271
00:17:16,550 --> 00:17:17,140
Thank you, mister.

272
00:17:43,790 --> 00:17:44,490
Everyone out.

273
00:17:51,230 --> 00:17:51,960
You too.

274
00:17:52,400 --> 00:17:52,850
Yes.

275
00:18:02,710 --> 00:18:03,370
Linglong,

276
00:18:05,470 --> 00:18:07,270
even if you quarreled with your father,

277
00:18:08,120 --> 00:18:09,580
you shouldn't have run away from home.

278
00:18:10,750 --> 00:18:12,290
Do you know how worried I was?

279
00:18:12,900 --> 00:18:13,610
It seems my father

280
00:18:13,610 --> 00:18:14,720
didn't tell you the truth.

281
00:18:16,470 --> 00:18:17,600
I didn't leave home

282
00:18:17,920 --> 00:18:18,960
because we argued.

283
00:18:19,810 --> 00:18:21,120
I simply don't want to marry you.

284
00:18:23,310 --> 00:18:23,960
Linglong.

285
00:18:56,180 --> 00:19:00,260
[Huo Linglong, eldest daughter of Linglong Manor]

286
00:19:20,340 --> 00:19:20,960
Let go.

287
00:19:22,680 --> 00:19:24,030
You left without a word for so many days.

288
00:19:24,550 --> 00:19:25,970
Martial Uncle Huo has been worried sick.

289
00:19:26,230 --> 00:19:27,340
I told him.

290
00:19:27,510 --> 00:19:28,660
If anyone tried to force me into marriage, I'd leave.

291
00:19:28,920 --> 00:19:29,770
If he refused to believe me, that's his own fault.

292
00:19:30,030 --> 00:19:31,580
If you didn't want to marry me so soon,

293
00:19:31,710 --> 00:19:32,860
you could've told me.

294
00:19:33,200 --> 00:19:34,220
I could've spoken to His Highness

295
00:19:34,220 --> 00:19:35,270
and postponed the wedding for a few months.

296
00:19:35,440 --> 00:19:36,770
There was no need to make such a scene.

297
00:19:36,880 --> 00:19:38,250
I'll say this one last time.

298
00:19:38,360 --> 00:19:39,680
I do not want to marry you.

299
00:19:42,840 --> 00:19:44,360
Whether you want to marry me or not,

300
00:19:45,130 --> 00:19:46,160
you're coming back with me.

301
00:19:46,800 --> 00:19:48,040
We can clear everything up

302
00:19:48,040 --> 00:19:48,880
in front of Martial Uncle Huo.

303
00:19:49,390 --> 00:19:50,130
Clear everything up?

304
00:19:53,390 --> 00:19:54,570
Are you taking me back

305
00:19:54,830 --> 00:19:56,220
to discuss the marriage,

306
00:19:56,630 --> 00:19:57,980
or because of the thing in my hands?

307
00:20:00,300 --> 00:20:01,280
I came here

308
00:20:01,280 --> 00:20:02,910
only because I was worried about your safety.

309
00:20:02,910 --> 00:20:04,220
Why were you hunting down Zhan Zhao?

310
00:20:08,550 --> 00:20:10,220
Yes, I received orders to capture him.

311
00:20:11,110 --> 00:20:12,570
I was only following orders.

312
00:20:13,590 --> 00:20:14,020
Linglong,

313
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:15,400
you've only just entered the outside world.

314
00:20:15,400 --> 00:20:16,530
You know nothing about people.

315
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:17,920
How can you trust a man

316
00:20:17,920 --> 00:20:19,460
you've only known for two or three days?

317
00:20:19,630 --> 00:20:20,980
Don't you think that's reckless?

318
00:20:22,040 --> 00:20:23,920
You've probably been dazzled

319
00:20:23,920 --> 00:20:24,660
by the title of Southern Hero

320
00:20:25,070 --> 00:20:26,240
and fooled

321
00:20:26,240 --> 00:20:27,220
by his righteousness act.

322
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:28,610
Besides,

323
00:20:28,800 --> 00:20:29,330
how do you even know

324
00:20:29,330 --> 00:20:30,770
he's the real Southern Hero Zhan Zhao?

325
00:20:31,310 --> 00:20:32,330
Whether he is or not,

326
00:20:33,390 --> 00:20:34,290
you know the answer.

327
00:20:35,920 --> 00:20:37,530
What I've seen in these few days is more

328
00:20:37,760 --> 00:20:39,180
than I saw in over ten years inside the manor.

329
00:20:40,360 --> 00:20:42,080
I can tell perfectly well who's truly righteous and who's only pretending.

330
00:20:42,550 --> 00:20:43,050
Linglong.

331
00:20:44,440 --> 00:20:44,850
Fine.

332
00:20:46,440 --> 00:20:47,610
I'm not as eloquent as you are, Linglong.

333
00:20:48,550 --> 00:20:49,450
As you said,

334
00:20:49,450 --> 00:20:50,860
Zhan Zhao is a good man.

335
00:20:51,070 --> 00:20:52,310
He helps the weak wherever he goes.

336
00:20:52,310 --> 00:20:53,020
I was wrong.

337
00:20:53,110 --> 00:20:54,160
I shouldn't have obeyed orders blindly

338
00:20:54,160 --> 00:20:54,940
without knowing right from wrong.

339
00:20:55,760 --> 00:20:56,740
I apologize to you.

340
00:20:58,720 --> 00:21:00,260
But have you thought about this?

341
00:21:00,630 --> 00:21:01,360
Mo Dao and the others

342
00:21:01,360 --> 00:21:02,810
are no honorable heroes.

343
00:21:03,080 --> 00:21:04,600
If Zhan Zhao is humiliated

344
00:21:04,600 --> 00:21:05,500
and tortured to death,

345
00:21:05,680 --> 00:21:06,630
then no matter how much injustice

346
00:21:06,630 --> 00:21:07,930
exists in this world,

347
00:21:08,790 --> 00:21:10,570
he'll never see it again, let alone stop it.

348
00:21:12,000 --> 00:21:14,020
Maybe Zhan Zhao only accepted this task because a friend asked him to.

349
00:21:14,150 --> 00:21:16,020
For just one word from a friend,

350
00:21:16,110 --> 00:21:17,420
he may die at the hands

351
00:21:17,600 --> 00:21:18,640
of a bunch of nameless thugs.

352
00:21:18,640 --> 00:21:19,900
Wouldn't that be too tragic?

353
00:21:27,240 --> 00:21:28,290
Before this,

354
00:21:28,830 --> 00:21:30,420
I probably would've agreed with you.

355
00:21:31,310 --> 00:21:33,110
But what exactly does this evidence involve,

356
00:21:33,240 --> 00:21:34,350
whether you've been working with others

357
00:21:34,350 --> 00:21:35,250
to falsely accuse Zhan Zhao,

358
00:21:36,960 --> 00:21:38,500
everything will become clear

359
00:21:38,590 --> 00:21:39,610
once the evidence reaches the court.

360
00:21:40,440 --> 00:21:41,570
So why are you in such a hurry

361
00:21:42,280 --> 00:21:43,750
to send so many people after him?

362
00:21:46,280 --> 00:21:47,370
Looks to me like

363
00:21:47,480 --> 00:21:49,740
you're after the thing in my hands.

364
00:21:49,830 --> 00:21:50,700
When you wear a mask for too long,

365
00:21:50,790 --> 00:21:51,660
can you still take it off?

366
00:21:51,870 --> 00:21:52,700
How dare you!

367
00:21:52,790 --> 00:21:53,290
Finally showing your true colors?

368
00:21:54,310 --> 00:21:55,570
Then you should think carefully.

369
00:21:56,000 --> 00:21:56,660
If you offend me,

370
00:21:57,280 --> 00:21:58,970
do you think you'll obtain the Linglong Eye from the Huo family?

371
00:21:59,310 --> 00:22:00,370
What are you talking about?

372
00:22:01,680 --> 00:22:02,290
I want to marry you

373
00:22:02,320 --> 00:22:03,390
because we care for each other.

374
00:22:03,390 --> 00:22:04,740
What does the Linglong Eye have to do with it?

375
00:22:04,800 --> 00:22:06,290
Everyone knows

376
00:22:06,870 --> 00:22:08,370
the Huo family's dowry

377
00:22:08,440 --> 00:22:09,810
is the heirloom known as the Linglong Eye.

378
00:22:10,440 --> 00:22:11,060
You rushed into this engagement for it,

379
00:22:11,060 --> 00:22:11,980
didn't you?

380
00:22:13,150 --> 00:22:14,530
There's no shame in admitting it.

381
00:22:15,040 --> 00:22:15,810
Huo Linglong,

382
00:22:16,960 --> 00:22:18,660
I'll give you one last chance.

383
00:22:19,200 --> 00:22:20,290
I've shown enough respect

384
00:22:20,390 --> 00:22:22,020
to you and Linglong Manor.

385
00:22:22,240 --> 00:22:23,770
Stop resisting and come back with me,

386
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:25,610
and I'll pretend none of this happened.

387
00:22:25,830 --> 00:22:26,940
And if I refuse?

388
00:22:27,110 --> 00:22:28,050
You won't escape

389
00:22:28,440 --> 00:22:29,420
from me.

390
00:22:50,900 --> 00:22:51,770
Hand it over,

391
00:22:51,770 --> 00:22:52,420
and come back with me.

392
00:22:52,470 --> 00:22:53,040
Never.

393
00:22:53,140 --> 00:22:54,230
You've only known him for two days,

394
00:22:54,230 --> 00:22:55,130
yet you're already risking your life for him.

395
00:22:55,760 --> 00:22:56,480
Have you

396
00:22:56,480 --> 00:22:57,630
developed feelings for him?

397
00:22:57,680 --> 00:22:58,370
That's nonsense.

398
00:22:59,240 --> 00:23:00,500
There's nothing between us.

399
00:23:00,680 --> 00:23:01,530
It'd better stay that way.

400
00:23:02,070 --> 00:23:03,170
His Soaring Crane Skill

401
00:23:03,170 --> 00:23:05,180
is the secret martial art of the Ding family of Songjiang Prefecture.

402
00:23:05,720 --> 00:23:06,940
Zhan Zhao's surname isn't Ding.

403
00:23:08,250 --> 00:23:09,660
He may well be the Ding family's

404
00:23:09,680 --> 00:23:10,560
future son-in-law.

405
00:23:11,240 --> 00:23:11,770
I hope

406
00:23:11,870 --> 00:23:13,290
you won't make a fool of yourself.

407
00:23:14,070 --> 00:23:15,980
If you refuse to hand it over,

408
00:23:16,550 --> 00:23:18,020
I'll have to take it myself.

409
00:23:31,380 --> 00:23:33,960
[Bai Yutang, Sleek Rat]

410
00:23:33,960 --> 00:23:34,880
Sorry about that.

411
00:23:35,680 --> 00:23:36,850
My hand slipped.

412
00:23:37,280 --> 00:23:37,770
Please carry on.

413
00:23:39,480 --> 00:23:40,420
What are you laughing at?

414
00:23:40,920 --> 00:23:42,050
I'm laughing

415
00:23:42,150 --> 00:23:43,020
because you're a grown man,

416
00:23:43,440 --> 00:23:44,700
yet fighting a woman

417
00:23:44,700 --> 00:23:45,900
smaller and weaker than you,

418
00:23:46,000 --> 00:23:46,700
and still struggling so much.

419
00:23:47,280 --> 00:23:47,960
Isn't that amusing?

420
00:23:48,870 --> 00:23:50,130
How long have you been watching?

421
00:23:50,240 --> 00:23:52,050
I've been here eating plums all along.

422
00:23:52,150 --> 00:23:53,020
You two barged in,

423
00:23:53,630 --> 00:23:55,500
making noise, shouting, and fighting.

424
00:23:56,000 --> 00:23:57,370
My family matters

425
00:23:58,000 --> 00:23:59,460
disturbed your peace.

426
00:23:59,720 --> 00:24:00,740
Please forgive us.

427
00:24:00,830 --> 00:24:02,260
Stop talking nonsense.

428
00:24:04,240 --> 00:24:05,570
He's a despicable man.

429
00:24:05,680 --> 00:24:06,420
I have nothing to do with him.

430
00:24:07,070 --> 00:24:07,660
I know.

431
00:24:09,070 --> 00:24:10,530
I accidentally overheard your conversation.

432
00:24:11,630 --> 00:24:12,900
His purpose here

433
00:24:13,110 --> 00:24:14,190
isn't to force you into marriage.

434
00:24:14,370 --> 00:24:15,940
It's the thing you're carrying.

435
00:24:16,920 --> 00:24:19,500
I advise you not to meddle in this.

436
00:24:20,280 --> 00:24:21,700
Getting on my bad side

437
00:24:21,790 --> 00:24:22,940
for some stranger

438
00:24:23,480 --> 00:24:24,460
is hardly worth it.

439
00:24:24,720 --> 00:24:25,770
I think you misunderstand.

440
00:24:26,200 --> 00:24:27,460
I never said I was going to interfere.

441
00:24:27,550 --> 00:24:28,460
You're not going to help her?

442
00:24:31,070 --> 00:24:32,180
Why should I?

443
00:24:32,550 --> 00:24:33,900
Her martial arts are a cut above you.

444
00:24:34,350 --> 00:24:35,900
Beating someone like you should be effortless for her.

445
00:24:35,920 --> 00:24:36,730
Why would she need my help?

446
00:24:45,310 --> 00:24:45,850
Miss,

447
00:24:46,390 --> 00:24:47,460
you possess fine skills.

448
00:24:47,550 --> 00:24:48,810
How come you can't beat him?

449
00:24:48,920 --> 00:24:49,810
That hardly makes sense.

450
00:24:50,590 --> 00:24:51,700
Please don't mock me, sir.

451
00:24:52,150 --> 00:24:53,180
I'm no match for him.

452
00:24:53,440 --> 00:24:53,900
What's there to fear?

453
00:24:54,440 --> 00:24:55,700
With just a little guidance from me,

454
00:24:55,790 --> 00:24:56,530
you'll be able to beat him.

455
00:24:58,200 --> 00:25:00,330
I wonder if this gentleman here has the patience

456
00:25:00,440 --> 00:25:01,290
and generosity for that.

457
00:25:01,760 --> 00:25:03,460
I know her skills well.

458
00:25:04,350 --> 00:25:05,570
If you want to enlighten her,

459
00:25:06,830 --> 00:25:07,420
go ahead.

460
00:25:11,590 --> 00:25:12,570
What exactly are you trying to do?

461
00:25:12,830 --> 00:25:13,770
What else?

462
00:25:14,000 --> 00:25:15,130
You've been too slow to realize things.

463
00:25:15,390 --> 00:25:16,130
I'm simply instructing you a little.

464
00:25:20,150 --> 00:25:21,500
I really can't beat him.

465
00:25:22,680 --> 00:25:24,500
We've sparred many times since childhood,

466
00:25:24,590 --> 00:25:25,330
and I've never once won.

467
00:25:25,520 --> 00:25:26,700
That was sparring before.

468
00:25:26,790 --> 00:25:27,600
This is life and death.

469
00:25:27,600 --> 00:25:28,500
It's kill or be killed.

470
00:25:28,870 --> 00:25:29,600
You're too focused on winning.

471
00:25:29,600 --> 00:25:30,610
That's why you can't beat him.

472
00:25:30,790 --> 00:25:31,610
What you should be thinking about

473
00:25:32,310 --> 00:25:33,130
is how to kill him.

474
00:25:36,680 --> 00:25:38,020
My leg is injured now.

475
00:25:38,150 --> 00:25:38,980
No way I can kill him.

476
00:25:39,360 --> 00:25:40,980
What does your leg injury have to do with anything?

477
00:25:41,000 --> 00:25:42,090
You must fight with all you have

478
00:25:42,280 --> 00:25:43,460
and overcome your fear.

479
00:25:44,480 --> 00:25:46,090
Weapons are meant for killing.

480
00:25:46,200 --> 00:25:46,660
Wield it

481
00:25:46,760 --> 00:25:48,260
with the resolve to kill.

482
00:25:48,550 --> 00:25:50,370
Fight until one side dies.

483
00:25:50,590 --> 00:25:51,290
Besides,

484
00:25:51,790 --> 00:25:53,330
you're holding a great weapon.

485
00:25:54,390 --> 00:25:55,810
That's a fine swordbreaker.

486
00:25:56,630 --> 00:25:58,090
Even if he fights you head-on,

487
00:25:58,200 --> 00:25:59,370
his sword can't withstand your weapon.

488
00:25:59,480 --> 00:26:00,530
So what is there to fear now?

489
00:26:16,200 --> 00:26:17,090
It's been so long.

490
00:26:17,200 --> 00:26:18,260
Why hasn't Commander Shao returned yet?

491
00:26:19,040 --> 00:26:20,610
Can catching a young lady be that difficult?

492
00:26:20,660 --> 00:26:22,370
Airhead.

493
00:26:23,280 --> 00:26:24,420
That's Commander Shao's

494
00:26:24,420 --> 00:26:26,180
bride.

495
00:26:27,040 --> 00:26:28,090
How could he use force?

496
00:26:28,790 --> 00:26:31,130
He has to coax her gently

497
00:26:31,630 --> 00:26:32,370
to bring her back.

498
00:26:32,790 --> 00:26:33,500
Should we

499
00:26:33,790 --> 00:26:35,020
go back and take a look?

500
00:26:35,680 --> 00:26:36,330
Are you insane?

501
00:26:36,590 --> 00:26:37,370
If you go back now

502
00:26:37,830 --> 00:26:38,610
and interrupt them

503
00:26:38,720 --> 00:26:39,220
whispering sweet words,

504
00:26:39,630 --> 00:26:40,610
he'll smash your head open.

505
00:26:41,630 --> 00:26:42,740
Think carefully.

506
00:26:43,550 --> 00:26:45,530
This time, I won't show mercy.

507
00:26:45,790 --> 00:26:46,220
Funny.

508
00:26:47,000 --> 00:26:48,090
Neither will I.

509
00:27:06,650 --> 00:27:07,330
That's more like it.

510
00:27:07,830 --> 00:27:09,220
Now that's your real skill.

511
00:27:09,390 --> 00:27:10,700
Linglong, you're serious?

512
00:27:11,000 --> 00:27:11,700
I told you

513
00:27:11,760 --> 00:27:12,610
I wouldn't show mercy.

514
00:27:13,040 --> 00:27:14,260
You belittle me.

515
00:27:18,040 --> 00:27:19,090
Pretentious.

516
00:27:19,280 --> 00:27:19,940
Don't be afraid of him.

517
00:27:54,630 --> 00:27:57,300
Looks like you backed the wrong side.

518
00:28:08,480 --> 00:28:10,610
Didn't you say you wouldn't interfere?

519
00:28:10,830 --> 00:28:11,810
Are you going back on your word?

520
00:28:13,150 --> 00:28:15,260
To be honest, someone asked me

521
00:28:15,520 --> 00:28:16,810
to escort this young lady

522
00:28:16,920 --> 00:28:17,260
safely back to the capital.

523
00:28:18,350 --> 00:28:19,500
You mean Zhan Zhao?

524
00:28:19,590 --> 00:28:19,980
That's right.

525
00:28:20,870 --> 00:28:21,640
After he was injured,

526
00:28:21,640 --> 00:28:23,020
he sent me a carrier pigeon,

527
00:28:23,110 --> 00:28:23,920
asking me to come help.

528
00:28:24,350 --> 00:28:25,580
You are...

529
00:28:25,750 --> 00:28:26,930
Didn't you say

530
00:28:27,240 --> 00:28:28,350
Zhan Zhao's Soaring Crane Skill

531
00:28:28,350 --> 00:28:29,420
is a secret art of the Ding family?

532
00:28:29,920 --> 00:28:31,460
The Ding Duo?

533
00:28:31,680 --> 00:28:32,330
Precisely.

534
00:28:32,630 --> 00:28:33,810
I'm Ding Zhaohui.

535
00:28:34,350 --> 00:28:35,930
My brother Ding Zhaolan and the others

536
00:28:35,930 --> 00:28:37,130
are on their way here.

537
00:28:37,630 --> 00:28:38,620
As you yourself just said,

538
00:28:39,080 --> 00:28:40,570
Zhan Zhao is the Ding family's future son-in-law.

539
00:28:40,870 --> 00:28:42,050
If anything happens to him,

540
00:28:42,051 --> 00:28:48,225
(Watch on www.kisskh.xyz Support Admin)

541
00:28:42,150 --> 00:28:42,710
the Ding family

542
00:28:42,710 --> 00:28:44,020
can't stand by and do nothing.

543
00:28:44,680 --> 00:28:45,740
I believe you've gotten the taste

544
00:28:45,740 --> 00:28:47,020
of Zhan Zhao's Soaring Crane Skill.

545
00:28:47,110 --> 00:28:48,050
He's mastered it like the back of his hand.

546
00:28:48,150 --> 00:28:49,500
He's nearly on par with my brother.

547
00:28:49,640 --> 00:28:50,190
As for me,

548
00:28:51,000 --> 00:28:51,850
I'm slightly weaker.

549
00:28:52,310 --> 00:28:53,750
But more than enough to hold you off for a while.

550
00:28:53,920 --> 00:28:54,850
Once my brother arrives,

551
00:28:55,070 --> 00:28:55,980
you can have a spar with him.

552
00:29:31,520 --> 00:29:31,980
So?

553
00:29:32,630 --> 00:29:33,850
What do you think

554
00:29:34,000 --> 00:29:34,570
of my Soaring Crane Skill?

555
00:29:39,590 --> 00:29:40,850
You are Zhan Zhao's friend?

556
00:29:41,200 --> 00:29:41,810
I know

557
00:29:42,000 --> 00:29:42,900
you want to rescue Zhan Zhao.

558
00:29:43,150 --> 00:29:43,770
But there are probably

559
00:29:43,870 --> 00:29:45,610
a whole pack of lackeys following behind him.

560
00:29:46,070 --> 00:29:47,090
We need to think of a plan.

561
00:29:47,550 --> 00:29:48,330
Besides,

562
00:29:48,440 --> 00:29:49,500
your leg is injured.

563
00:29:49,720 --> 00:29:51,020
It's not safe to linger here.

564
00:29:51,110 --> 00:29:51,900
We should leave first.

565
00:29:54,550 --> 00:29:55,090
Strange.

566
00:29:57,310 --> 00:29:58,260
Where did they go?

567
00:30:25,150 --> 00:30:26,050
This was torn

568
00:30:26,150 --> 00:30:26,610
from Commander Shao's robe.

569
00:30:26,900 --> 00:30:30,180
[Exchange the hostage at Luosi Cave outside Jiang Village at dawn tomorrow]

570
00:30:30,870 --> 00:30:31,130
This is bad.

571
00:30:31,790 --> 00:30:32,660
Commander Shao's been captured.

572
00:30:33,000 --> 00:30:33,420
Quick. Let's go.

573
00:30:33,530 --> 00:30:34,020
Let's go.

574
00:30:34,270 --> 00:30:34,610
Go.

575
00:31:03,480 --> 00:31:04,570
Apply these herbs

576
00:31:04,580 --> 00:31:05,460
to your wound.

577
00:31:05,720 --> 00:31:06,370
They'll ease the pain

578
00:31:06,400 --> 00:31:07,610
and help it heal faster.

579
00:31:09,480 --> 00:31:09,980
Thank you.

580
00:31:12,070 --> 00:31:13,090
You know healing skills too?

581
00:31:13,310 --> 00:31:14,180
I travel around a lot.

582
00:31:14,630 --> 00:31:15,970
I picked up a few ways

583
00:31:16,000 --> 00:31:16,850
to treat minor injuries and bruises.

584
00:31:17,630 --> 00:31:18,390
Your leg injury

585
00:31:18,390 --> 00:31:19,530
can't handle another tough fight

586
00:31:19,630 --> 00:31:20,460
like earlier.

587
00:31:20,650 --> 00:31:21,420
If we want to rescue Zhan Zhao,

588
00:31:21,520 --> 00:31:23,220
we'll need a quick and decisive plan.

589
00:31:23,720 --> 00:31:24,520
Didn't you say

590
00:31:24,520 --> 00:31:25,470
your brother was coming

591
00:31:25,660 --> 00:31:26,570
with helpers?

592
00:31:27,440 --> 00:31:28,420
I lied to him.

593
00:31:28,530 --> 00:31:29,180
You actually believed it?

594
00:31:29,760 --> 00:31:30,460
So everything you said

595
00:31:30,490 --> 00:31:31,420
was a lie?

596
00:31:31,660 --> 00:31:32,740
Most of it was true.

597
00:31:33,390 --> 00:31:34,180
For instance,

598
00:31:34,280 --> 00:31:35,260
you being able to beat him.

599
00:31:35,350 --> 00:31:35,980
That part was true.

600
00:31:36,920 --> 00:31:38,130
But the winner is decided.

601
00:31:38,390 --> 00:31:39,500
So that statement is false.

602
00:31:39,600 --> 00:31:40,980
Victory and defeat aren't decided in a single battle.

603
00:31:42,040 --> 00:31:42,980
After this fight,

604
00:31:43,040 --> 00:31:45,020
you've broken the fear you had of him.

605
00:31:45,200 --> 00:31:46,730
Defeating him is only a matter of time now.

606
00:31:46,900 --> 00:31:47,570
Besides,

607
00:31:48,200 --> 00:31:49,260
that fellow's talent

608
00:31:49,350 --> 00:31:50,130
has pretty much reached its limit.

609
00:31:50,350 --> 00:31:51,980
I doubt he'll improve any further.

610
00:31:55,200 --> 00:31:57,020
You said that you're Ding Zhaohui.

611
00:31:57,350 --> 00:31:58,260
Was that true or false?

612
00:31:58,680 --> 00:31:59,610
Of course it's true.

613
00:32:00,110 --> 00:32:01,500
My family and the Zhan family have been close for generations.

614
00:32:01,590 --> 00:32:02,660
We grew up together.

615
00:32:03,200 --> 00:32:04,060
My sister

616
00:32:04,060 --> 00:32:05,220
has been betrothed to him since childhood.

617
00:32:05,390 --> 00:32:05,920
My father even taught him

618
00:32:05,920 --> 00:32:08,090
our family's secret art, Soaring Crane Skill.

619
00:32:08,390 --> 00:32:09,740
They may not be married yet,

620
00:32:10,200 --> 00:32:11,500
but he'll be my brother-in-law.

621
00:32:12,140 --> 00:32:13,130
If you want to ask about him,

622
00:32:13,720 --> 00:32:14,770
there's plenty I can tell you.

623
00:32:23,420 --> 00:32:26,860
[Exchange the hostage at Luosi Cave outside Jiang Village at dawn tomorrow]

624
00:32:32,790 --> 00:32:33,460
Chief Zhong,

625
00:32:33,550 --> 00:32:34,850
say something.

626
00:32:37,480 --> 00:32:38,370
Commander Shao

627
00:32:38,520 --> 00:32:39,260
is a great hero.

628
00:32:40,070 --> 00:32:41,290
How could he possibly be captured

629
00:32:42,110 --> 00:32:42,770
by some young girl?

630
00:32:44,240 --> 00:32:46,310
Apparently, this was torn from his robe.

631
00:32:46,310 --> 00:32:47,290
How could it be fake?

632
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:48,900
We searched all around the dock,

633
00:32:49,050 --> 00:32:50,180
but didn't find a single trace of him.

634
00:32:50,760 --> 00:32:51,740
If nothing happened to him,

635
00:32:51,830 --> 00:32:52,850
what else could it be?

636
00:32:53,280 --> 00:32:54,370
We went to great lengths

637
00:32:54,480 --> 00:32:55,500
to capture

638
00:32:55,590 --> 00:32:56,260
Zhan Zhao.

639
00:32:56,680 --> 00:32:57,740
How could we let him go easily?

640
00:32:58,240 --> 00:32:59,770
Master ordered

641
00:33:00,200 --> 00:33:01,500
that Zhan Zhao must not leave Xiangzhou.

642
00:33:02,630 --> 00:33:04,740
Master values Commander Shao greatly.

643
00:33:04,960 --> 00:33:06,370
He would never leave him to die.

644
00:33:10,200 --> 00:33:11,810
In that case, send someone back

645
00:33:12,390 --> 00:33:13,450
and ask Master for instructions

646
00:33:13,640 --> 00:33:14,480
before we decide what to do.

647
00:33:15,080 --> 00:33:16,680
The kidnapper said the hostage exchange

648
00:33:16,680 --> 00:33:17,650
will happen at dawn tomorrow.

649
00:33:17,880 --> 00:33:18,700
If we send someone back now,

650
00:33:19,030 --> 00:33:20,180
it'll take time for them to return.

651
00:33:20,420 --> 00:33:21,330
What exactly are you implying?

652
00:33:21,490 --> 00:33:22,420
Commander Shao's safety

653
00:33:22,760 --> 00:33:23,420
matters,

654
00:33:23,590 --> 00:33:24,660
but does Master's order

655
00:33:25,070 --> 00:33:25,770
not matter?

656
00:33:31,080 --> 00:33:31,690
What brings you here?

657
00:33:33,940 --> 00:33:35,730
Master thought you might be short-handed,

658
00:33:36,230 --> 00:33:37,320
so he sent me over.

659
00:33:40,750 --> 00:33:41,980
I thought

660
00:33:42,350 --> 00:33:43,620
once Zhan Zhao was captured,

661
00:33:44,140 --> 00:33:45,350
the matter

662
00:33:45,350 --> 00:33:46,490
was nearly settled.

663
00:33:47,830 --> 00:33:49,660
Who would've thought the kidnapping of Shao Jizu

664
00:33:49,660 --> 00:33:51,070
would throw you all into chaos like headless chickens?

665
00:33:51,540 --> 00:33:52,730
Mr. Zhi Hua,

666
00:33:52,880 --> 00:33:53,660
care to share

667
00:33:54,160 --> 00:33:55,010
your clever plan

668
00:33:55,640 --> 00:33:57,210
with us

669
00:33:57,210 --> 00:33:57,730
headless chickens?

670
00:33:58,550 --> 00:33:59,680
If you had captured Zhan Zhao

671
00:33:59,680 --> 00:34:00,700
back in Yicheng County,

672
00:34:01,270 --> 00:34:02,210
would any of this

673
00:34:02,210 --> 00:34:03,010
have happened afterward?

674
00:34:03,750 --> 00:34:04,980
Even if the sky falls,

675
00:34:05,160 --> 00:34:06,400
I shouldn't be the one

676
00:34:06,400 --> 00:34:07,290
rushing to hold it up.

677
00:34:07,990 --> 00:34:09,530
If the thing in Zhan Zhao's hands

678
00:34:10,150 --> 00:34:11,570
reaches the imperial court,

679
00:34:12,190 --> 00:34:13,220
then

680
00:34:13,720 --> 00:34:15,170
the sky will fall.

681
00:34:16,280 --> 00:34:17,050
If Master's years of endeavor in Xiangzhou

682
00:34:17,080 --> 00:34:19,210
are ruined because of him,

683
00:34:19,210 --> 00:34:20,570
everyone sitting here

684
00:34:21,280 --> 00:34:22,260
will be buried alongside him.

685
00:34:26,280 --> 00:34:26,860
Mr. Zhi,

686
00:34:27,470 --> 00:34:28,740
say whatever you need to say.

687
00:34:29,670 --> 00:34:30,780
As long as we can rescue Commander Shao,

688
00:34:31,670 --> 00:34:32,530
except for certain people,

689
00:34:33,070 --> 00:34:34,010
everyone in the prefectural yamen

690
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:35,170
will be at your disposal.

691
00:34:35,400 --> 00:34:36,570
At the battle at West Bridge Dock,

692
00:34:36,800 --> 00:34:38,970
you captured the Southern Hero

693
00:34:39,550 --> 00:34:41,340
and suffered internal injuries because of it.

694
00:34:41,920 --> 00:34:42,570
This time,

695
00:34:43,470 --> 00:34:44,490
you should stay here.

696
00:34:45,150 --> 00:34:46,490
Can half of the Iron Blood Guards here

697
00:34:46,630 --> 00:34:47,300
be reassigned

698
00:34:47,590 --> 00:34:48,470
to accompany

699
00:34:48,470 --> 00:34:49,760
Feng Shao and me?

700
00:35:20,510 --> 00:35:21,050
Well?

701
00:35:21,150 --> 00:35:22,130
Any suspicious people?

702
00:35:22,800 --> 00:35:23,570
Not even a fly.

703
00:35:24,070 --> 00:35:25,010
Could we have come to the wrong place?

704
00:35:26,670 --> 00:35:27,220
That can't be right.

705
00:35:27,960 --> 00:35:28,940
The blood letter clearly stated

706
00:35:29,030 --> 00:35:30,340
the hostage exchange would take place outside Jiang Village.

707
00:35:31,280 --> 00:35:32,420
Check the riverside.

708
00:35:33,470 --> 00:35:33,900
That makes sense.

709
00:35:34,150 --> 00:35:34,900
Let's head to the riverside.

710
00:35:35,070 --> 00:35:35,530
Yes.

711
00:35:53,920 --> 00:35:54,700
There's a boat over there.

712
00:35:54,990 --> 00:35:55,650
Go take a look.

713
00:36:04,720 --> 00:36:05,170
Commander Shao!

714
00:36:09,240 --> 00:36:10,010
You fell for it!

715
00:36:10,050 --> 00:36:11,050
Hurry back!

716
00:36:11,050 --> 00:36:11,680
Go back!

717
00:36:18,030 --> 00:36:18,860
Where's Zhong Xiong?

718
00:36:19,510 --> 00:36:20,180
Zhong Xiong!

719
00:36:21,570 --> 00:36:22,230
Need some help.

720
00:36:22,230 --> 00:36:22,740
Quick.

721
00:36:28,910 --> 00:36:29,490
Careful.

722
00:36:32,550 --> 00:36:33,160
What happened?

723
00:36:33,360 --> 00:36:34,380
How did this happen?

724
00:37:11,760 --> 00:37:13,280
So many people guarding one man.

725
00:37:13,390 --> 00:37:14,900
Looks like his crimes are pretty serious.

726
00:38:00,920 --> 00:38:01,420
Zhan!

727
00:38:04,550 --> 00:38:04,970
Zhan.

728
00:38:25,280 --> 00:38:26,010
You all go first.

729
00:38:26,190 --> 00:38:26,970
I'll catch up later.

730
00:38:56,260 --> 00:38:58,060
[Yanling]

731
00:39:48,300 --> 00:39:49,490
I'm taking Zhan Zhao with me.

732
00:39:49,800 --> 00:39:51,700
If you know what's best for you, save your strength

733
00:39:51,700 --> 00:39:52,490
and stop struggling.

734
00:40:21,030 --> 00:40:22,220
Are you sure there were two of them?

735
00:40:22,760 --> 00:40:23,780
One was dressed in white?

736
00:40:23,780 --> 00:40:24,170
Yes.

737
00:40:24,720 --> 00:40:25,570
The other one

738
00:40:25,990 --> 00:40:27,530
carried an incredibly powerful weapon.

739
00:40:27,630 --> 00:40:28,610
It's Yinyang An.

740
00:40:29,240 --> 00:40:29,820
Commander Shao,

741
00:40:30,400 --> 00:40:31,640
why didn't you say earlier

742
00:40:31,910 --> 00:40:32,840
that Zhan Zhao's accomplice

743
00:40:32,840 --> 00:40:33,970
was from Linglong Manor?

744
00:40:34,590 --> 00:40:35,610
Aren't you engaged

745
00:40:35,610 --> 00:40:36,490
to them?

746
00:40:36,640 --> 00:40:38,170
Why would they help outsiders instead?

747
00:40:38,670 --> 00:40:40,720
Linglong was misled for a moment by scheming people.

748
00:40:40,880 --> 00:40:41,460
That explains why

749
00:40:41,460 --> 00:40:42,900
Commander Shao's earlier pursuits

750
00:40:42,900 --> 00:40:43,820
all failed.

751
00:40:44,470 --> 00:40:45,300
Could it be

752
00:40:46,030 --> 00:40:47,680
you were holding back

753
00:40:47,680 --> 00:40:48,900
because of your engagement to Linglong Manor?

754
00:40:50,070 --> 00:40:51,680
This time was my mistake.

755
00:40:53,070 --> 00:40:54,420
But how did they know

756
00:40:54,630 --> 00:40:56,010
Zhan Zhao was imprisoned here?

757
00:40:56,960 --> 00:40:57,900
Chief Zhong,

758
00:40:58,240 --> 00:41:00,010
did you pull all the Iron Blood Guards from the checkpoints

759
00:41:00,240 --> 00:41:02,130
after we left?

760
00:41:02,550 --> 00:41:03,220
Of course.

761
00:41:04,280 --> 00:41:05,420
We had found that fellow.

762
00:41:06,110 --> 00:41:07,530
Why keep my men there any longer?

763
00:41:12,070 --> 00:41:13,970
So they followed the Iron Blood Guards here.

764
00:41:14,440 --> 00:41:16,300
Who exactly is that young man in white?

765
00:41:17,280 --> 00:41:19,450
He's young, but incredibly skilled and bold.

766
00:41:19,800 --> 00:41:21,220
The first time I met him,

767
00:41:21,800 --> 00:41:23,420
he claimed to be Ding Zhaohui.

768
00:41:23,880 --> 00:41:24,660
Ding Zhaohui?

769
00:41:24,720 --> 00:41:25,300
Impossible.

770
00:41:25,960 --> 00:41:26,970
I've fought with him.

771
00:41:27,800 --> 00:41:29,450
His martial arts have nothing in common with the Ding family's.

772
00:41:30,070 --> 00:41:31,170
He wasn't telling the truth.

773
00:41:32,400 --> 00:41:33,820
His martial arts are exceptional,

774
00:41:33,990 --> 00:41:34,780
and his style is unusual.

775
00:41:35,880 --> 00:41:37,300
I can't tell which sect his skills come from.

776
00:41:38,070 --> 00:41:39,010
His qinggong is excellent.

777
00:41:39,470 --> 00:41:40,380
He's no less skilled

778
00:41:40,760 --> 00:41:41,610
than the Huo family.

779
00:41:42,360 --> 00:41:42,610
Hyah!

780
00:41:44,240 --> 00:41:44,570
Hyah!

781
00:41:48,960 --> 00:41:50,170
Where are we headed?

782
00:41:50,590 --> 00:41:51,940
West Bridge Dock?

783
00:41:52,320 --> 00:41:54,490
Perhaps we can cross the river before they catch up.

784
00:41:54,760 --> 00:41:55,560
They're riding

785
00:41:55,560 --> 00:41:57,050
fine horses provided by the authorities.

786
00:41:57,960 --> 00:41:59,450
We're in a carriage

787
00:41:59,590 --> 00:42:01,010
with a badly injured man.

788
00:42:01,280 --> 00:42:02,700
How could we possibly outrun them?

789
00:42:02,920 --> 00:42:03,860
On top of that,

790
00:42:04,320 --> 00:42:05,420
the one inside

791
00:42:05,670 --> 00:42:06,970
can't take much more of this.

792
00:42:21,030 --> 00:42:21,940
His pulse is extremely weak.

793
00:42:22,720 --> 00:42:23,900
Not much different from a dead man.

794
00:42:40,190 --> 00:42:41,010
What did you give him?

795
00:42:41,920 --> 00:42:42,530
Linglong Honey.

796
00:42:43,920 --> 00:42:45,050
It may not save his life,

797
00:42:45,280 --> 00:42:46,450
but at least it'll ease his pain.

798
00:42:47,440 --> 00:42:48,220
Does it even help?

799
00:42:49,030 --> 00:42:49,840
"Love at First Sight" inside him

800
00:42:49,840 --> 00:42:50,970
has seeped into his bones.

801
00:42:51,760 --> 00:42:52,570
What do we do about that?

802
00:42:55,550 --> 00:42:56,420
Why are you so concerned about him?

803
00:42:58,840 --> 00:42:59,340
Give me a hand.

804
00:43:30,860 --> 00:43:36,340
♪In this martial world, true friends are rare♪

805
00:43:37,020 --> 00:43:41,740
♪Yet some would fight by my side♪

806
00:43:41,900 --> 00:43:43,900
♪Across towering mountains♪

807
00:43:43,940 --> 00:43:48,940
♪Risking all for peace beneath the heavens♪

808
00:43:49,820 --> 00:43:56,220
♪If we face life and death together, why fear the hard road ahead?♪

809
00:43:56,300 --> 00:44:02,780
♪Roaming this endless martial road♪

810
00:44:02,940 --> 00:44:09,180
♪Seeing the world's joy and sorrow pass by♪

811
00:44:09,380 --> 00:44:12,420
♪Honor still burns within us♪

812
00:44:12,540 --> 00:44:18,620
♪Still, love and grudges are the hardest to escape♪

813
00:44:18,860 --> 00:44:23,300
♪Too tangled to let go♪

814
00:44:24,820 --> 00:44:29,060
♪Who says loyalty and honor can't coexist?♪

815
00:44:29,060 --> 00:44:32,740
♪One swing of the sword ends it all♪

816
00:44:33,060 --> 00:44:38,660
♪My heart stays true, just as before♪

817
00:44:39,260 --> 00:44:44,380
♪Right and wrong will reveal themselves♪

818
00:44:44,740 --> 00:44:49,620
♪Why let others decide for us?♪

819
00:44:49,860 --> 00:44:54,060
♪If this journey has no way back♪

820
00:44:54,260 --> 00:44:57,660
♪Then there's no need for sorrow♪

821
00:44:58,460 --> 00:45:04,420
♪Let a lone boat carry me past the mountains♪

822
00:45:04,860 --> 00:45:10,100
♪One last glance, and the clouds are gone♪

823
00:45:10,100 --> 00:45:15,700
♪The bright moon will light my way home♪

824
00:45:16,380 --> 00:45:23,180
♪The bright moon will light my way home♪
